Clone drupal-10-compatibility branch for Drupal 10. A new release will be created when the Drupal 10 is ready. The intention is to maintain separate versions of this module until Drupal 10 evolves.

The 8.x-1.x-dev version of this module currently works on Drupal 10 and is being tested against Drupal 10 on a weekly basis. See https://www.drupal.org/pift-ci-job/2285065 for the most recent test results. The intention is to keep the development version of this module in sync with changes to core Drupal as Drupal 10 evolves.
